Class PropertyDefinitionBuilder

  • Object
    • PropertyDefinitionBuilder
  • public class PropertyDefinitionBuilder
extends Object
    This class allows you to create new PropertyDefinition objects in a fluent manner, setting only the actual information you required. Invoke build() after setting the attributes to obtain the created object.
